title: San Bruno Charming Home with Spacious Garden and Deck
posting_body: ['You will love this charming home with bench seating at entry.', ' Walk into a spacious living room with fireplace and hardwood floors throughout.', ' A split level two bedrooms one bath home with an expansive living room with fireplace upon entry.', ' This is a sweet home with dining room and kitchen with French doors open to deck with BBQ and lush garden perfect for indoor/outdoor living.', ' Gas stove, dishwasher, kitchen sink overlooks a side entry window and lots of cabinets for storage.', '  Off the living room, the interior stairs lead to 2 bedrooms 1 bath on upper level.', ' A large bedroom at front, a second bedroom overlooking garden and a full updated bath with natural stone off the hallway.', 'This rental is maintained by a gardener with mature trees; a lemon tree and flowering pants with a lush green lawn.', ' Enjoy picturesque views to the garden from the interior back rooms; bedroom, dining room, and kitchen accessed thru glass paneled french doors.', ' This is a sweet and comfortable home.', ' Garage parking with electric garage door opener and lots of storage, washer/dryer with interior access from the 1 car garage.', '  Small dog ok.', 'A tree lined street, this home is in close proximity  to The Avenue neighborhood shopping, Mollie Stones, Bay Hill Shopping Center and Fitness.', ' One block to San Bruno Park, minutes away from 280 fwy access bordering Millbrae for easy commute.', "  Don't miss viewing this charming home for immediate move in.", ' Text to confirm your weekend showing.']
